ORIGINAL MATERIALS ATTRIBUTION:

This digital implementation is based on the Theory of Mind Booklet Task
originally developed by Hilary Richardson, Grace Lisandrelli,
Alexa Riobueno-Naylor, and Rebecca Saxe.

Original materials are available at: https://osf.io/g5zpv/

When using this assessment in research, please cite:

Richardson, H., Lisandrelli, G., Riobueno-Naylor, A., & Saxe, R. (2018).
Development of the social brain from age three to twelve years.
Nature Communications, 9(1), 1027.

Richardson, H., Lisandrelli, G., Riobueno-Naylor, A., & Saxe, R. (2020).
Open dataset of theory of mind reasoning in early to middle childhood.
Scientific Data, 7(1), 386.
